<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">٢٦:</span> وقالوا: <span class="c1">"يا حرزا وأبتغي النوافلا"</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أي أحرزت ما أريد، وأنا أبتغي الزيادة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">٢٧:</span> وقالوا: <span class="c1">"كلاهما وتمرا"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">٢٨:</span> وقالوا: <span class="c1">"احلب حلباً لك شطره"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">٢٩:</span> وقالوا: <span class="c1">"كفى قوماً بصاحبهم خبيرا"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">٣٠:</span> ومثله: <span class="c1">"أتعلمني بضب أنا حرشته"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">٣١:</span> ومثله: <span class="c1">"أنا ابن بجدتها"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>